Detailed Description

Base class for all processors which need a lot of AHcal specific data, like the CALICE::IntegratedHcalCalibrationProcessor and the CALICE::IntegratedHcalDigitizationProcessor.

Author:
Sebastian Schmidt

bool CALICE::IntegratedHcalProcessor::_cellCalibUsedGainTempCorr [protected]

This flags shows whether the current cell is calibrated or digitized with a temperature corrected mip constant or not.

This should be set and only set in getGain. USE WITH CARE!
